==== 东部锦龟 ====
东部锦龟分布于加拿大东南部至美国佐治亚州，[[阿帕拉契山脉|阿帕拉契山脉]]以东的地方，而其中位于分布区最北的锦龟往往被局限在靠近大西洋的较温暖地带活动。在美国，东部锦龟在新罕布什尔州最北的地方则不常见，而在缅恩州也只见于离海岸线50英里内一带区域<ref name="NHFG range">{{cite web|title=Eastern painted turtle|url=http://www.wildlife.state.nh.us/Wildlife/Nongame/turtles/painted_turtle.htm|publisher=New Hampshire Fish and Game Department|accessdate=2011-02-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927221018/http://www.wildlife.state.nh.us/Wildlife/Nongame/turtles/painted_turtle.htm|archivedate=2011-09-27}}</ref><ref name=Hunter>{{cite book|last=Hunter|first=Malcom L.|title=Maine amphibians and reptiles|year=1999|publisher=University of Maine Press|isbn=978-0-89101-096-8|coauthors=Calhoun, Aram J. K.; McCollough, Mark}} as cited by {{cite web|title=Amphibians and reptiles|url=http://www.dlwa.org/docs/reptiles_and_amphibians.pdf|publisher=Damariscotta Lake Watershed Association|accessdate=2011-02-10|archive-date=2012-08-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69gtV6UEn?url=http://www.dlwa.org/docs/reptiles_and_amphibians.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在加拿大，东部锦龟分布在新不伦瑞克省和新斯科舍省，魁北克省和爱德华王子岛则没有分布。在美国南部的南、北卡罗来纳州的沿海[[低地|低地]]、佐治亚州南部和整个佛罗里达州也没有分布{{sfn|Ernst|Lovich|2009|p=185}}<ref name=Conant/>{{sfn|Carr|1952|p=215}}。

